---
import SectionContainer from "@/components/SectionContainer.astro";
---

<SectionContainer id="why-us" class="mt-4">
  <div class="why-us-wrapper">
    <!-- Layout tipo revista con sidebar -->
    <div class="sidebar-title">
      <div class="vertical-text">
        <span class="vertical-label">Por qué elegirnos</span>
        <h2 class="vertical-heading">De nuestra fábrica a tu hogar</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar-decoration"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main content con timeline visual -->
    <div class="content-area">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <p class="intro-paragraph">
          Con <strong>cariño y responsabilidad</strong>, cada pieza que creamos
          cuenta una historia de compromiso con la calidad y el medio ambiente.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Features con diseño timeline/lista numerada -->
      <div class="features-timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="marker-number">1</span>
            <div class="marker-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="content-icon">
              <svg
                width="40"
                height="40"
                viewBox="0 0 48 48"
                fill="none"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              >
                <path
                  d="M24 6C18.48 6 14 10.48 14 16C14 19.12 15.44 21.9 17.68 23.72C14.12 25.36 11.44 28.8 10.48 32.96C10.24 34.04 10.92 35.08 12 35.32C13.08 35.56 14.12 34.88 14.36 33.8C15.48 28.92 19.32 26 24 26C28.68 26 32.52 28.92 33.64 33.8C33.84 34.68 34.6 35.28 35.44 35.28C35.6 35.28 35.76 35.24 35.92 35.2C37 34.96 37.68 33.92 37.44 32.84C36.48 28.68 33.8 25.24 30.24 23.6C32.48 21.78 33.92 19 33.92 15.88C34 10.48 29.52 6 24 6ZM24 10C27.32 10 30 12.68 30 16C30 19.32 27.32 22 24 22C20.68 22 18 19.32 18 16C18 12.68 20.68 10 24 10Z"
                  fill="currentColor"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="content-text">
              <h3 class="content-title">Madera maciza ecológica</h3>
              <p class="content-description">
                Solo trabajamos con madera ecológica con certificado PEFC de
                bosques de pino insignis cultivados en nuestra zona.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="marker-number">2</span>
            <div class="marker-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="content-icon">
              <svg
                width="40"
                height="40"
                viewBox="0 0 48 48"
                fill="none"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              >
                <path
                  d="M38 12H34V10C34 7.8 32.2 6 30 6H18C15.8 6 14 7.8 14 10V12H10C7.8 12 6 13.8 6 16V38C6 40.2 7.8 42 10 42H38C40.2 42 42 40.2 42 38V16C42 13.8 40.2 12 38 12ZM18 10H30V12H18V10ZM38 38H10V16H38V38ZM24 20C20.7 20 18 22.7 18 26C18 29.3 20.7 32 24 32C27.3 32 30 29.3 30 26C30 22.7 27.3 20 24 20ZM24 28C22.9 28 22 27.1 22 26C22 24.9 22.9 24 24 24C25.1 24 26 24.9 26 26C26 27.1 25.1 28 24 28Z"
                  fill="currentColor"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="content-text">
              <h3 class="content-title">Envíos en 1 semana</h3>
              <p class="content-description">
                Nos comprometemos a que tu pedido salga de fábrica como tarde en
                1 semana para que lo puedas disfrutar cuanto antes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="marker-number">3</span>
            <div class="marker-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="content-icon">
              <svg
                width="40"
                height="40"
                viewBox="0 0 48 48"
                fill="none"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              >
                <path
                  d="M24 6C14.06 6 6 14.06 6 24C6 33.94 14.06 42 24 42C33.94 42 42 33.94 42 24C42 14.06 33.94 6 24 6ZM24 38C16.28 38 10 31.72 10 24C10 16.28 16.28 10 24 10C31.72 10 38 16.28 38 24C38 31.72 31.72 38 24 38ZM25 16H22V26L30.5 31.1L32 28.6L25 24.2V16Z"
                  fill="currentColor"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="content-text">
              <h3 class="content-title">Diseñamos y fabricamos</h3>
              <p class="content-description">
                Asumimos todo el proceso de diseño y fabricación para que
                nuestros muebles tengan el mejor precio posible.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="marker-number">4</span>
            <div class="marker-line last"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="content-icon">
              <svg
                width="40"
                height="40"
                viewBox="0 0 48 48"
                fill="none"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              >
                <path
                  d="M36 18C36 16.9 35.1 16 34 16H14C12.9 16 12 16.9 12 18V30C12 31.1 12.9 32 14 32H34C35.1 32 36 31.1 36 30V18ZM34 30H14V18H34V30ZM24 20C21.8 20 20 21.8 20 24C20 26.2 21.8 28 24 28C26.2 28 28 26.2 28 24C28 21.8 26.2 20 24 20Z"
                  fill="currentColor"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="content-text">
              <h3 class="content-title">Devoluciones gratuitas</h3>
              <p class="content-description">
                Tienes un plazo de 15 días para realizar devoluciones. Nuestro
                equipo de atención al cliente, te ayudará en lo que necesites.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</SectionContainer>

<style>
  .why-us-wrapper {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 2rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Sidebar con texto vertical */
  .sidebar-title {
    position: sticky;
    top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .vertical-text {
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    text-orientation: mixed;
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .vertical-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .vertical-heading {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .sidebar-decoration {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .deco-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent);
  }

  .deco-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  /* Content Area */
  .content-area {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .intro-text {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-secondary);
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .intro-paragraph {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .intro-paragraph strong {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Timeline Features */
  .features-timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Timeline Marker */
  .timeline-marker {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .marker-number {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    z-index: 2;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .marker-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    position: absolute;
    top: 48px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .marker-line.last {
    display: none;
  }

  /* Timeline Content */
  .timeline-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .content-icon {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-item:hover .content-icon {
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: white;
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .content-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .content-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
  }

  .content-description {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .why-us-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }

    .sidebar-title {
      position: static;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .vertical-text {
      writing-mode: horizontal-tb;
      transform: none;
    }

    .vertical-label {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .sidebar-decoration {
      flex-direction: row;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .deco-line {
      width: 100px;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .why-us-wrapper {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .sidebar-title {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .sidebar-decoration {
      display: none;
    }

    .content-area {
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .intro-text {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      border-left-width: 2px;
    }

    .intro-paragraph {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .features-timeline {
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .marker-number {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .marker-line {
      top: 42px;
    }

    .timeline-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .content-icon {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
    }

    .content-icon svg {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .why-us-wrapper {
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .vertical-heading {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .content-area {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .intro-text {
      padding-left: 1rem;
    }

    .intro-paragraph {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .features-timeline {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .marker-number {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .marker-line {
      top: 36px;
      width: 1px;
    }

    .content-icon {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
    }

    .content-icon svg {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
    }

    .content-title {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .content-description {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
  }
</style>
